Dialogue: 100,0:00:20.74,0:00:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dnă profesoară Celia,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:22.70,0:00:26.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}au trecut trei zile de când am părăsit capitala regală Beltrant.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:26.97,0:00:28.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Am ajuns în siguranță într-un regat vecin,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}orașul Amande, mai exact, care este un oraș comercial din Regatul Galarc.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.77,0:00:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu se regăsește aici... nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.18,0:00:42.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cum în capitala regală eram deja în afișele cu persoane căutate,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:42.99,0:00:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mi-a fost greu să fac rost de lucrurile necesare pentru călătoria mea,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:46.35,0:00:48.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}dar se pare că nu au ajuns încă în acest oraș,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:48.94,0:00:50.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}deci, te rog să nu-ți faci griji pentru mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.52,0:00:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amande este un oraș plin de viață.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:55.54,0:00:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mâncarea este din belșug
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.28,0:01:00.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}și se pare că voi reuși să fac rost de alimente durabile, ceea ce e o ușurare.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:07.21,0:01:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bănuiesc că sunt prea tensionat.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:46.81,0:02:48.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bun venit!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:49.07,0:02:50.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Avem supă cu paste!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:50.88,0:02:53.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Un bol doar opt monede mici de cupru!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:53.93,0:02:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai spus cumva... paste?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:56.07,0:02:59.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce? Băiete, ești pentru prima oară în acest oraș?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:59.18,0:03:00.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ei bine, da.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:01.28,0:03:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Supă cu paste! Domnișoara Liselotte, persoana care guvernează acest oraș,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:05.26,0:03:08.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a creat un produs din grâu numit "tăieței", care este folosit în acest fel de mâncare.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:09.65,0:03:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Liselotte...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Așa arată după ce este preparat.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:14.35,0:03:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mulțumesc pentru așteptare!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:15.84,0:03:16.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Paste...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:17.45,0:03:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Este prima oară când văd așa ceva în această lume.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:19.81,0:03:21.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Și am mai auzit și cuvântul "tăieței".
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.47,0:03:26.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arată bine, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:26.00,0:03:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și este și foarte gustos!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:27.75,0:03:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Atunci, pot primi o porție, vă rog?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:29.32,0:03:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mulțumesc că ați comandat!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:36.73,0:03:37.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este extrem de bun!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.91,0:03:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:40.28,0:03:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Așa o aromă nostalgică.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:44.20,0:03:48.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oare această Liselotte este din aceeași lume precum Haruto?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:49.91,0:03:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nu că ar conta acum.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:51.90,0:03:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nu e ca și cum s-ar schimba ceva dacă mă voi gândi la asta.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:57.92,0:04:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Când vei crește, te voi duce acolo. Este un locul numit Yagumo. {ep1}
Dialogue: 100,0:04:03.40,0:04:05.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Serios? E o promisiune. {ep1}
Dialogue: 100,0:04:06.50,0:04:07.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vreau...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.17,0:04:11.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vreau să văd locul natal al părinților mei.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.73,0:04:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Făcusem acea promisiune cu mama mea.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:17.13,0:04:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acela este?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.70,0:04:21.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vrei să cumperi tăieței?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:21.74,0:04:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da. Cred că va fi bine să am cu mine în călătoria mea.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:24.99,0:04:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, și mâncarea a fost foarte bună.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:27.30,0:04:30.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,În acest caz, mergi pe acel drum până ajungi la breasla de negustori Ricca.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:31.12,0:04:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ar trebui să vezi o coadă lungă la magazinul cu ghifle la aburi{greșeala intenționată} de la primul etaj,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:34.18,0:04:35.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,deci sunt sigur că o vei recunoaște imediat.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.15,0:04:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai spus... ghifle la aburi?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.50,0:04:41.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da! Este un alt produs inventat de domnișoara Liselotte...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:41.33,0:04:42.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este bună, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.70,0:04:43.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:43.75,0:04:47.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Două ghifle la aburi cu carne și una cu brânză!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:47.47,0:04:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vă mulțumim pentru așteptare!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:49.23,0:04:51.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sunt fierbinți, deci, vă rog să aveți grijă.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:51.68,0:04:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chifle la aburi cu carne?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:53.44,0:04:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Și asta îmi trezește un sentiment de nostalgie.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.58,0:04:58.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Salutare și bun venit la breasla de negustori Ricca.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vă mulțumim foarte mult.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sperăm să mai treceți pe la noi curând.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.17,0:05:05.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Domnule?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:06.07,0:05:10.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vă cerem să nu aveți o sabie asupra dumneavoastră în incinta magazinului.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:10.37,0:05:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vă puteți lăsa lucrurile de o parte, iar noi vom avea grijă de ele.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, mulțumesc.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:16.87,0:05:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are părul negru?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.63,0:05:21.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Așa voi face.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:21.88,0:05:24.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vă mulțumim pentru înțelegere.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:24.38,0:05:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu te voi servi astăzi. Numele meu este Lotte.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:42.51,0:05:43.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Intră.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Scuză-mă.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.07,0:05:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mulțumesc că m-ai așteptat.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:47.61,0:05:51.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cincisprezece kilograme de paste și zece kilograme de orz.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:51.94,0:05:55.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ți-am pregătit și niște condimente și câteva ustensile pentru gătit.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.75,0:05:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Serios? Mulțumesc.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.66,0:06:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Le-am pus într-un rucsac mare, care este destul de greu.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:04.11,0:06:06.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Te vei descurca cu el pe drumul spre casă?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:07.06,0:06:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Servește-te, te rog.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:08.14,0:06:09.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mulțumesc.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.67,0:06:13.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poate nu pare, dar am făcut ceva antrenamente fizice. Nu trebuie să-ți faci griji.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:17.23,0:06:19.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai mai băut ceai negru până acum?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:23.48,0:06:26.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Printre cunoștințele mele există o domnișoară care iubește ceaiul negru.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:26.50,0:06:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am învățat multe lucruri de la ea în timp ce beam împreună ceai negru.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:29.53,0:06:33.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,În acest caz, îți poți da seama ce fel de frunze au fost folosite?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:35.65,0:06:38.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Această aromă unică și astringența ușoară...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:39.74,0:06:44.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sunt cumva frunze din Lis? Folosiți frunze foarte bune aici.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:44.48,0:06:45.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vesela, de asemenea.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:45.75,0:06:49.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ca să avem parte de cele mai bune discuții alături de clienții noștri,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.08,0:06:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,mediul în care acestea au loc trebuie să fie cât mai bun cu putință.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.76,0:06:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acesta este mottoul breselei noastre de negustori!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:55.21,0:07:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,În acest caz... vrei să ne ocupăm noi de livrarea scrisorii tale?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:01.72,0:07:02.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.77,0:07:07.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Și astfel am reușit să cumpăr tot ce mi-am propus, iar acum sunt pe cale să pornesc la drum.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.54,0:07:11.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}După ce voi părăsi regiunea Strahl, nu voi mai putea trimite scrisori,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.33,0:07:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}dar, te rog să nu-ți faci griji.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Faptul că nu auzi nimic de mine înseamnă că sunt bine.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:16.88,0:07:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am pornit la drum.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.40,0:07:19.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haruto.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.60,0:07:21.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drum bun.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îți mulțumesc pentru tot ajutorul.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.91,0:07:32.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce băiat misterios, nu-i așa, domnișoară Liselotte?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:32.22,0:07:35.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acum sunt Lotte, Cosette.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.22,0:07:37.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Așa este.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:45.22,0:07:46.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Un copil?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:46.75,0:07:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, ești bine?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otravă?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.99,0:08:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Un om-bestie?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.18,0:08:13.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Te voi...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.67,0:08:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ucide.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:20.04,0:08:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Trebuie să neutralizez otrava sau altfel...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.66,0:08:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îmi cer scuze. Nu te pot lăsa să mă omori.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.99,0:08:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otrava nu a funcționat?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:38.77,0:08:39.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Este rapidă!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enchant Physical Ability!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.55,0:08:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She hadn't already enhanced her \Nphysical abilities with magic?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:54.88,0:08:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that movement...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.70,0:08:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How fast will she be after enhancing?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:06.83,0:09:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why... Why is this person...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.31,0:09:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's human. Why is he so fast?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.29,0:09:28.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's too focused on the knife.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.47,0:09:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is as far as it goes. \NYou understand me, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:51.63,0:09:54.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No... No!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:55.11,0:09:56.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:56.99,0:09:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Calm down!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:00.83,0:10:04.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Help me! Mom!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.24,0:10:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I suppose I have no choice.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:18.94,0:10:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Collar of Submission?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:26.38,0:10:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The magic in that book...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dispell, was it?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:32.33,0:10:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I imitate that, will this come off?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:50.99,0:10:54.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Latifa! Wake up!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Latifa...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:03.40,0:11:05.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Latifa?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.03,0:11:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Endo Suzune.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:07.69,0:11:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you still half-asleep?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:18.97,0:11:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Latifa...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:21.29,0:11:23.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What am I to you?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:24.20,0:11:26.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am your esteemed older brother, Stewart.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:26.28,0:11:28.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, say, "my esteemed older brother"!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:30.27,0:11:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I don't want—
Dialogue: 100,0:11:36.46,0:11:40.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It hurts! It hurts! It hurts! It hurts!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:40.17,0:11:42.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Esteemed older brother." Say it!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:43.52,0:11:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-Esteemed older brother...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. Wake up.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:55.07,0:11:57.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop that. Your hands and legs are bound.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems you understand the situation.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:01.31,0:12:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to die, \Ndon't get violent like you did earlier.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:07.08,0:12:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I don't fight, then you won't kill me?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:10.35,0:12:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That depends on you.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:13.80,0:12:15.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you come here from Beltrant?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:17.24,0:12:18.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:18.25,0:12:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know what this is?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:20.47,0:12:22.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A... collar?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's... gone!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:26.34,0:12:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:27.47,0:12:31.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This collar was the reason \Nyou were obeying orders, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:32.13,0:12:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You won't be stricken with pain any more.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:49.27,0:12:53.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the collar is gone, you won't have \Nany problems answering my questions, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:55.02,0:12:57.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who gave you your orders?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:59.63,0:13:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You and I are the only \Nones here. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:02.63,0:13:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know my master's name.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:06.75,0:13:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never been told, so...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:09.52,0:13:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't even know the name of their house?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:11.55,0:13:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The name of the house?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:14.93,0:13:18.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But I do know the name of \Nmy esteemed older brother!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:18.43,0:13:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said it was Stewart!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:20.61,0:13:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stewart... Is he a beast person, like you?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:24.63,0:13:27.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My older brother is human.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:27.54,0:13:29.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The human who trained me.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:30.15,0:13:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Human...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:32.09,0:13:33.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, it must be him.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:34.61,0:13:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's that commoner who's responsible!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fearing that the truth may come to light,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:39.93,0:13:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Duke Huguenot decided to make me disappear.\N Thinking about it that way,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:43.37,0:13:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}everything seems consistent, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:47.47,0:13:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are there others besides \Nyou trying to kill me?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:50.97,0:13:53.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:53.06,0:13:56.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't think so... probably.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:57.07,0:13:58.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:58.02,0:13:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,here is my final question.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:59.94,0:14:00.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:01.98,0:14:05.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you still intend to kill me?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:08.05,0:14:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't k-kill you!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:11.13,0:14:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do as you like, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:13.05,0:14:16.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've left all your equipment \Nwith that robe over there.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:19.97,0:14:22.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It means you're free to run away.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:23.56,0:14:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the collar that controlled you is gone,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:26.71,0:14:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there's no need for you \Nto go back to your master.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:30.89,0:14:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But here in Strahl, where \Nbeast people are made slaves,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:34.67,0:14:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there is nowhere safe for this girl.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:38.09,0:14:40.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you leave this kingdom \Nand head to the east,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:40.41,0:14:42.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there is a vast area known as the Wilderness.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:44.42,0:14:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhere in that place,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:45.95,0:14:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there is a land where beast people like \Nyou and other demi-humans live together.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:51.35,0:14:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Wilderness? East...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:54.41,0:14:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The direction I've been traveling.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:58.19,0:15:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead of staying here,
Dialogue: 100,0:15:00.20,0:15:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,looking for others of your kind there \Nmight be an easier way for you to live.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:02.92,0:15:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Others of my kind. East. Wilderness.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:08.88,0:15:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be going, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:10.59,0:15:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you this. The next time \Nyou attack me, I won't show any mercy.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:26.49,0:15:28.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you still have some \Nkind of business with me?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-Um, east...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:31.49,0:15:34.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to go with you.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:35.67,0:15:38.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seem to have misunderstood.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:38.67,0:15:42.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't release you from your enslavement \Nbecause I wanted to rescue you.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:44.21,0:15:48.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only that not killing you was \Nmore convenient for me. That's all.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:48.39,0:15:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But... I don't know what I should do.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:53.61,0:15:58.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm human, just like \Nthe people who enslaved you.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you scared?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:01.09,0:16:03.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't feel... bad.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:03.98,0:16:08.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You believe I would think nothing \Nof you trying to kill me?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:14.32,0:16:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:16.70,0:16:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm angry.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:19.23,0:16:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You couldn't disobey your \Norders is all, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:23.18,0:16:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's no guarantee that \Nyou won't attack me again.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:28.80,0:16:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In short, I can't trust you.\N Do you understand?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:31.76,0:16:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, th-this collar! You can put it on me!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:36.12,0:16:39.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mind! So please...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:39.51,0:16:42.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why did you bring that?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:42.02,0:16:44.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You hated having that collar on, didn't you?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:45.41,0:16:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate being alone like this more.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:49.82,0:16:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:51.61,0:16:52.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:56.27,0:16:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right. Do what you want.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, I will!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:02.91,0:17:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get rid of that collar.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:04.94,0:17:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:07.60,0:17:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Latifa.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:13.57,0:17:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Rio.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Latifa.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:17.79,0:17:19.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:28.31,0:17:30.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:30.52,0:17:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't need to apologize \Nfor something like that.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:33.33,0:17:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:34.22,0:17:36.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm allowed to eat that?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:36.47,0:17:38.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. No need to be polite.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:44.67,0:17:46.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:46.22,0:17:47.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:52.45,0:17:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one's going to steal it from you.\N Take your time eating.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:56.37,0:18:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My meals... They said it was pet food... \NEvery day, my older brother would...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:09.14,0:18:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've just about reached the Wilderness.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not too hard for you?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:12.60,0:18:14.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've already crossed the border, so...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:18.74,0:18:22.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a little early, but let's make camp here.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:22.94,0:18:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:24.56,0:18:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I'm holding you back.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:27.75,0:18:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, you're not.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:36.58,0:18:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:38.15,0:18:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a letter from Rio!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:40.36,0:18:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad he seems well.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:42.32,0:18:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reaching Amande in three days...\NThat's so fast!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:45.71,0:18:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not receiving more news makes \Nme feel a little lonely, but..
Dialogue: 100,0:18:48.89,0:18:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope that, wherever you are \Non your journey, you are safe.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:58.51,0:19:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! Spaghetti?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:00.61,0:19:02.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know what this is?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:02.73,0:19:05.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! It's spaghetti!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:05.05,0:19:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I eat some?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:08.41,0:19:10.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for... the food!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:16.09,0:19:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've eaten pasta before?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:18.23,0:19:19.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:19.75,0:19:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, um... Yes, I used to eat it. I think.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:26.25,0:19:28.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you seemed accustomed to eating it.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:28.97,0:19:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's more. Eat as much as you want.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:32.99,0:19:34.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:35.78,0:19:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calling this pasta "spaghetti" means...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:38.51,0:19:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be that this girl is also...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:46.35,0:19:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:47.84,0:19:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't like this! Where am I?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:51.12,0:19:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:56.97,0:20:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right. It's not scary anymore.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:00.43,0:20:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom, Dad, Onii-san...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:04.29,0:20:06.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to go home to Tokyo...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:07.06,0:20:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokyo?!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:10.35,0:20:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There really is no mistake. \NThis girl is also...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:14.72,0:20:16.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-san...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rest easy. Sleep.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:38.91,0:20:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His hair is black.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:41.04,0:20:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He does look like him, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:45.17,0:20:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:48.09,0:20:51.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning. Did you sleep well?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:53.53,0:20:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:54.60,0:20:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Onii...Rio!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:58.10,0:21:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oni Rio?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:00.05,0:21:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, that's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:02.18,0:21:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was about to say "Onii-chan," and then...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:06.20,0:21:11.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rio, would you mind if \NI called you O-Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:11.00,0:21:11.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:12.11,0:21:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You d-don't want me to?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:13.90,0:21:16.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not that I mind, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:16.81,0:21:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom, Dad, Onii-san...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:20.47,0:21:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to go home to Tokyo...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:23.27,0:21:25.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A girl who was still so young
Dialogue: 100,0:21:25.74,0:21:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}reincarnated from Earth to \Nthis world and was made a slave.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:29.93,0:21:31.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She must have felt so alone.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:32.05,0:21:35.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If this will comfort her \Nheart even a little, then...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:54.60,0:21:55.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:55.58,0:21:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are we having for breakfast today?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:57.90,0:21:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want to eat, Latifa?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:59.84,0:22:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want omelets! With cheese in them!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:02.82,0:22:04.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Omelets, huh? All right.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:09.64,0:22:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Latifa?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:11.47,0:22:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really can't see that big \Ntree over there, can you?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:14.73,0:22:18.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one you were talking about yesterday?\NI can only see regular forest.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:18.65,0:22:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Latifa can't see it. That means...
Dialogue: 100,0:22:22.33,0:22:25.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it being blocked from people's \Nawareness through magic?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:27.35,0:22:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 100,0:22:28.89,0:22:31.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are we really going in there?\NWe won't get lost?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:31.90,0:22:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:36.58,0:22:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, it's very faint, \Nbut I smell something I don't recognize.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:41.27,0:22:42.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More than one scent.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:42.50,0:22:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it different from an animal's scent?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:45.05,0:22:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:47.59,0:22:51.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it's faint, whatever the scent \Nbelongs to isn't nearby, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:51.62,0:22:54.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:54.14,0:22:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, why don't we \Nrest around here for today?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:57.26,0:22:59.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our goal may be close by.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:59.64,0:23:01.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:23:01.18,0:23:03.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll finally be able to leave the forest!
Dialogue: 100,0:23:11.29,0:23:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is she having another nightmare?
Dialogue: 100,0:23:17.34,0:23:20.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With this, she won't have any scary dreams.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:31.90,0:23:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 100,0:23:36.38,0:23:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Pădurea Spiritelor."
